	"system": {
		"description": "<p>You have worked to hone your psychic focus, and it has become more potent than that of other espers. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Your Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma score increases by +1 to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>You gain an expertise die to the Insight skill. Your maximum expertise die for Insight becomes a d10.</p></li><li><p>You gain proficiency with the Arcana skill or an expertise die if you are already proficient.</p></li><li><p>You gain an additional noetic. It does not count against your noetics known.</p></li><li><p>When your psionic focus ends, you can choose to emit a pulse that deals [[/r 2d6]] points of psychic damage to creatures within 10 feet of you as a reaction.</p></li><li><p>While you are psionically-focused, you have truesight with a range of 5 feet.</p></li></ul>",
